      <title>中国工厂活动再次萎缩 给经济带来警告</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-30/china-factory-activity-shrinks-again-in-warning-to-economy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[6 月份，中国制造业活动连续第二个月萎缩，表明中国政府寄希望于推动经济发展的这一领域出现疲软迹象。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-30/china-factory-activity-shrinks-again-in-warning-to-economy</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 30 Jun 2024 01:51:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
