      <title>预计 2024 年下半年日本股市涨势将放缓</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-30/japan-s-stock-rally-is-forecast-to-slow-in-second-half-of-2024</link>
      <description><![CDATA[投资者预计日本股市上涨的速度将在下半年放缓，这增加了他们将更多资金转移到竞争市场的风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-30/japan-s-stock-rally-is-forecast-to-slow-in-second-half-of-2024</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 30 Jun 2024 01:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
